| **Glass‑Fiber Reinforced Polymer (GFRP)** | 1,800–2,000 | 300–800 | Good, but lower than CFRP; more brittle under impact | Good | Moderate – less demanding cure cycles than CFRP | Secondary structures, fairings, interior panels |
